items.name: Gemini 3.1 Pro
items.tagline: A smarter model for your most complex tasks
items.description: 3.1 Pro is designed for tasks where a simple answer isn‚Äôt enough. Building on the Gemini 3 series, 3.1 Pro represents a step forward in core reasoning. 3.1 Pro is a smarter, more capable baseline for complex problem-solving.

items.name: Google Pomelli - Photoshoot
items.tagline: Turn simple product photos into pro studio imagery instantly
items.description: Introducing Pomelli‚Äôs latest feature update, ‚ÄòPhotoshoot‚Äô. With Photoshoot, you can start from a single image of your product and easily create high quality, customized product shots to elevate your marketing. It also allows you to create and edit your own product images from scratch. Describe the image you want or upload any image as a reference to create custom assets quickly.

items.name: Architect by Lyzr
items.tagline: Build AI that works for you
items.description: What if N8N and Lovable Have a baby? Well, Architect is exactly that! Build powerful multi-agent AI systems where you can see and control every decision, every integration, every flow. Before writing a single line of code. No black boxes. No guesswork. Just clarity.

items.name: Claudebin
items.tagline: Export and share your Claude Code sessions as resumable URLs
items.description: Claude Code runs in your terminal. Session data is stored locally, but not in a human-readable format. If the session contains useful context, refactors, tool usage, reviewing or sharing it isn‚Äôt straightforward. Claudebin lets you export a Claude Code session. It captures: - the full message thread - file reads/writes - bash commands - web and MCP calls It returns a URL with a structured, navigable viewer. You can link it in a PR, embed a selected range in your docs, or resume it locally.

items.name: Arcmark
items.tagline: Your bookmarks, attached to any browser as a sidebar
items.description: A native macOS bookmark manager that attaches to any browser window as a sidebar. Open source, free, and local-first. Heavily inspired by Arc Browser's sidebar.

items.name: keychains.dev
items.tagline: Give AI access to 6754+ APIs with zero credentials exposed
items.description: Keychains.dev is a secure credential proxy for AI agents. Use "keychains curl" as a drop-in for curl ‚Äî just replace hard-coded credentials with template variables like {{GITHUB_TOKEN}}. Keychains injects real credentials server-side. Your agent never sees raw secrets ‚Äî immune to prompt injection by design. Users approve each permission with one click and can revoke access anytime. Full audit trail. Works with 11,000+ API providers (OAuth, API keys, basic auth).

items.name: Guideless
items.tagline: Create AI-narrated software video guides in minutes
items.description: We built Guideless out of frustration with existing walkthrough tools. Everything we tried felt bloated with unnecessary features and still produced mediocre output. So we obsessed over UX and output quality. We built effortless capture with auto-generated captions, added AI refinements, and a wide selection of natural-sounding, multi-language AI voiceovers. The result is on-brand guides that look clean, sound premium by default, and can be instantly shared, embedded, or exported to MP4.

items.name: NotchPrompt
items.tagline: The invisible teleprompter that lives in your MacBook Notch.
items.description: Stop looking down at your notes. NotchPrompt wraps your script directly around the MacBook camera notch, so you maintain perfect eye contact while reading. üëÅÔ∏è The killer feature? It is 100% invisible during screen sharing. Your audience on Zoom/Meet/Teams sees a clean desktop; only YOU see the text. Native Swift & SwiftUI Hardware-integrated Auto-scroll & Hotkeys 100% Free & Open Source.

items.name: Repaint
items.tagline: Build a website by chatting with AI
items.description: Repaint is an AI agent for building custom websites. It interviews you, imports info, finds design references, and generates a full site in minutes.

items.name: Merge
items.tagline: Use your Apple Watch with any Android phone
items.description: Merge finally brings the Apple Watch to Android. Unlock Apple Watch's cutting-edge health data on your Android phone, synced to any Health Connect compatible app. Get Android notifications on your wrist, reply to messages, control media playback, and more.
